         <abstract>
            <p>Various integrals relating to the $I_e$-function $$I_e(k, z) = \int^z_0 e^{-x}I_0(kx) dx,$$ which finds a wide variety of applications in the fields of statistical communication theory and noise analysis, are evaluated in closed form.</p>
          </abstract>
